This repository includes a Korean translation of:
“The Ultra-Scale Playbook: Training LLMs on GPU Clusters” (2025)
Authors: Nouamane Tazi, Ferdinand Mom, Haojun Zhao, Phuc Nguyen, Mohamed Mekkouri, Leandro Werra, Thomas Wolf
Source: https://huggingface.co/spaces/nanotron/ultrascale-playbook
License: Apache License 2.0

Modifications:
- Korean translation of the text
- Additional explanations/annotations for Korean readers
- Repository structure and build instructions for PDF

This is an unofficial translation. Original copyright and notices are preserved.


